[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0217","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0217.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0239","title":"Atrium Software Mercur WebView WebMail-Client 1.0 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Atrium Software Mercur WebView WebMail 服务器（1.0 版本）在处理 HTTP GET 请求时，对 mail_user 参数未做长度校验，存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者只需向目标服务器发送包含超长 mail_user 参数的特制 GET 请求，即可触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务崩溃并造成拒绝服务（DoS）。该漏洞影响运行 Mercur WebView WebMail-Client 1.0 的服务器，攻击条件仅需网络可达并能够发送 HTTP 请求，无需任何权限或用户交互，利用方式简单且可被远程自动化发起。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0239"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-03-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:17.810","remediation":"升级到 Atrium Software 发布的 Mercur WebView 修复版本（1.0 之后的安全更新版本），彻底替换存在漏洞的 1.0 版本；若无法升级，应在 Web 服务器或边界防火墙前端对发往 Mercur 服务的 GET 请求中 mail_user 参数的长度进行限制（如截断超过 256 字节的输入），并通过反向代理过滤超长请求头作为临时缓解措施，同时将该服务仅对内网开放以减少暴露面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=95325335825295&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1056","http://www.ussrback.com/labs36.html","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19810","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8f7915616bad1c7280e28216588ab0258074928/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0239.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0239","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0239.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ea13d8ca97b52327fe351b64da51866911834231/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0239.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5gjw-82fr-pgpf/GHSA-5gjw-82fr-pgpf.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/mercure_webview.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0239.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1056/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0217.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0217.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0217.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0175","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0175.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0198","title":"Atrium Software Mercur Mail Server 3.2 多个缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Atrium Software Mercur Mail Server 3.2 的 POP3 和 IMAP 服务存在多个缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向受影响服务发送特制超长请求即可触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务崩溃从而拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Mercur Mail Server 3.2 版本，攻击者可通过 110/TCP（POP3）或 143/TCP（IMAP）端口实施攻击，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0198"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-03-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:12.360","remediation":"立即升级 Mercur Mail Server 至 3.3 及以上版本（Atrium 在被 Ipswitch 收购前发布的最终修复版）。如产品已停止维护无法获取更新，应迁移至仍在安全支持周期内的邮件服务器（如 Ipswitch IMail 或 Exchange）。临时缓解措施：在防火墙层面限制 POP3(TCP 110)、IMAP(TCP 143) 和 SMTP(TCP 25) 仅允许受信 IP 访问，并在服务端关闭不必须的 POP3/IMAP 服务，减小攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/current/0137.html","http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/ntbugtraq/current/0206.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1051","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19807","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad08212eac84f46206c2da8a50436d48e5ad608c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0198.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2