vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0700.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0520","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0520.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0169","title":"Oracle Web Listener 4.0.x ows-bin 目录批处理文件远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Oracle Web Listener 4.0.x 的 ows-bin 目录中存在批处理文件，远程攻击者可通过向 URL 附加 '?&' 参数构造恶意请求，利用该漏洞在服务器上执行任意命令。攻击者无需身份认证即可通过网络远程触发，可能导致敏感信息泄露、系统被控制等严重后果。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0169"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2000-03-15","updated":"2000-03-15","remediation":"Oracle Web Listener 4.0.x 已停止维护，建议升级到 Oracle HTTP Server 或禁用 ows-bin 目录的批处理文件执行权限，限制对 ows-bin 目录的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T04:28:18.325871052+00:00","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/ntbugtraq/2000-q1/0211.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1053"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0520.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0520.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0520.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0158","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0158.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0180","title":"Generation Terrorists Designs & Concepts Sojourn 2.0 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Sojourn 搜索引擎 2.0 版本存在路径遍历漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向搜索功能提交包含 `../` 序列的特制请求，突破目录限制读取服务器上的任意文件，如配置文件、密码文件等敏感信息。该漏洞源于程序未对用户输入的路径参数进行充分过滤，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0180"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-03-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:10.033","remediation":"该漏洞年代久远，Sojourn 2.0 搜索引擎已停止维护，无官方补丁。建议立即停止使用该产品，迁移至其他受支持的搜索引擎方案；如无法替换，需在 Web 服务器层面配置 URL 重写规则，拦截包含 ../ 的路径遍历请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/ntbugtraq/2000-q1/0201.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1052","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/4197","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19808","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1d6385d398a2a41185d3cc14943c25f73c724ba3/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0180.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0180","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0180.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8b7c7b13d1542fc7ddfb9cf48e51f3de3ab5c4ab/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0180.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xqgx-493j-vhxr/GHSA-xqgx-493j-vhxr.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/sojourn.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0180.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0158.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0207","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0207.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0230","title":"imwheel 缓存区溢出本地提权漏洞","description":"imwheel 是 Linux 系统上用于鼠标滚轮支持的 X11 实用程序。该漏洞存在于 imwheel-solo 脚本中，由于对 HOME 环境变量的长度缺乏有效校验，导致本地攻击者可通过构造超长的 HOME 环境变量触发缓存区溢出。imwheel-solo 以 setuid root 权限运行，成功利用该漏洞可导致本地用户直接获取 root 权限，进而完全控制系统。该漏洞影响 Halloween Linux 4.0 以及 Red Hat Linux 6.1/6.2 等发行版。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0230"],"sources":["exploitdb","cve"],"published":"2000-03-13","updated":"2000-03-13","remediation":"升级 imwheel 软件包至已修复该漏洞的版本，确保 HOME 环境变量输入得到正确边界校验。对于仍在使用受影响发行版的系统，建议尽快升级至受支持的现代 Linux 发行版。同时，如非必要，可暂时移除 imwheel-solo 的 setuid 权限设置以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-03/0168.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-2000-016.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1060","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19812"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19812"],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0207.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0207.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0207.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0215","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0215.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0237","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 在启用 Web Publishing 功能时存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标服务器发送特制的 GET 请求访问 /publisher 目录，即可通过该目录提供的 Java applet 浏览服务器上的任意目录内容，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响启用 Web Publishing 功能的 Netscape Enterprise Server 版本，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。建议禁用 Web Publishing 功能或升级至修复版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0237"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-03-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:17.547","remediation":"立即禁用 Netscape Enterprise Server 的 Web Publishing 功能（在管理界面取消勾选 \"Enable Web Publishing\"），或升级至 iPlanet Web Server 6.0+ (SP5) 版本。如无法升级，应在 Web 服务器配置中限制 /publisher 目录访问权限，拒绝匿名 GET 请求。该产品已停止维护，建议迁移至 Oracle iPlanet Web Server 7.0+ 或 Apache httpd。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1075","http://zsh.stupidphat.com/advisory.cgi?000311-1","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad08212eac84f46206c2da8a50436d48e5ad608c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0237.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3